{"tid":2112444,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勸大家唔好再覆啲屌地區既post","createTime":"2020-07-17T10:22:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T13:22:50.000Z","uid":143347,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44c5fd85da93fa576f9c35052c774425ad2a53a1","tid":2112444,"uid":143347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:22:39.000Z","msg":"發現最近好多呢類無聊野上熱門<br />\n<br />\n一黎無意義 個個區都有黃店有手足 比你鬥黃贏左又點？贏左啲乜？<br />\n二黎地區連結係我地大家抗爭得到既野之一（類似士氣？團結？）<br />\n三黎一覆就知道你住邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港咁細 流動又大 某區有肺炎就度度都有機會有<br />\nJer住某啲區 跟著又屌到去公屋私樓 挑起曬你地啲火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（嗱 呢度起底又縮窄範圍）<br />\n<br />\n特別依家啲慈雲山金大仙post 呢區開花過咁多次 真係居心叵測<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望大家冷靜小心啲 無論對方係pr又好狗又好真心on9仔又好 無視佢地就岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d48b8d10c6234a8b8f64a56267ce4a15692b520","tid":2112444,"uid":143347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:27:03.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"890972bbcae2730053ba1cc0ad005b152e410d04","tid":2112444,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"屌廢老有乜嘢問題<br />\n利申 慈記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3866d5d2aaae425e2c274524d043f316e0b4cf7","tid":2112444,"uid":143347,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"890972bbcae2730053ba1cc0ad005b152e410d04","tid":2112444,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:27:36.000Z","msg":"屌廢老有乜嘢問題<br />\n利申 慈記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:32:12.000Z","msg":"廢老唔識上網 點解你又唔去兜口兜臉屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"802f37fb652bd3c0db6516896775ffdbc6007521","tid":2112444,"uid":143347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T10:46:12.000Z"